{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/11092", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/11092/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/11092/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/11092/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/11092", "id": 24656760, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUyNDY1Njc2MA==", "number": 11092, "title": "Implement attributes for branch weight", "user": {"login": "kvanbere", "id": 1356959, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjEzNTY5NTk=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1356959?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/kvanbere", "html_url": "https://github.com/kvanbere", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kvanbere/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kvanbere/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kvanbere/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kvanbere/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kvanbere/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kvanbere/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kvanbere/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kvanbere/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/kvanbere/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 113376, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwxMTMzNzY=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/I-slow", "name": "I-slow", "color": "e10c02", "default": false, "description": "Problems and improvements with respect to performance of generated code."}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 4, "created_at": "2013-12-21T00:54:12Z", "updated_at": "2018-06-08T03:42:01Z", "closed_at": "2017-04-15T06:07:54Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "The `cold` attribute exists for functions, but one might want to put weights on branches. This could have 3 forms; `weight=N` where N is 0-1, `likely` (1) and `unlikely` (0).\n\nLLVM understands these annotations on branches already and can use these to fine-tune assembly to reduce branch mis-predictions. By nature, these could be used extensively in the standard library.\n\nie\n\n```\nmatch leaf {\n    #[likely]\n    Some(x) => recurse(x),\n    None => {\n        // do stuff that doesn't make sense to be in a cold fn\n        ...\n    }\n}\n```\n\nThere have been cases in Haskell libraries where changing the order of ADTs can increase performance by around 20% because branches are guessed differently by the compiler.\n", "closed_by": {"login": "aturon", "id": 709807, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjcwOTgwNw==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/709807?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/aturon", "html_url": "https://github.com/aturon", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aturon/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aturon/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aturon/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aturon/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aturon/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aturon/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aturon/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aturon/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aturon/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/11092/reactions", "total_count": 4, "+1": 4, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-